{
  "stem": "5228.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we was staying there in-- in blocks, and sleeping of-- was three, like three floors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And five girls of one-- one bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if one fall down from the top, the whole-- all of us was down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, broken everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bleeding.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you often [INAUDIBLE] what else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, every morning, they took us out [INAUDIBLE] to counting if we are all here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One day, it was missing two girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They was lying someplace, dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They was thinking that they run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They kept us a whole day, outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got to kneel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was one Jewish woman-- I mean, we was all a Jewish there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She didn't want to kneel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She said, a Jewish woman shouldn't kneel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they beat her so-- I mean, we was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nobody moved.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They beat her to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But she didn't want to kneel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She said, I shouldn't kneel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was very bad this time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then they find the two girls, dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They just was going with a wagon and picking up, every morning, the dead people, and throw them over the wagon, like-- like in a-- like piece of wood.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody was skinny, and just half dead, [? with ?] us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this was twice a day, what they took us, and they count us, if everybody is there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "OK, after it happened, we got a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She helped to put us-- I mean, when they, the German, the SS, come in to count, to us that we stay straight and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then her sister, with husband, was some place hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They catch them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They brought them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they-- then her sister-- they put in the same barrack, [INAUDIBLE] us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
